{"tid":1857123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請記住 落實真雙普選先係現行嘅最大目標","createTime":"2020-02-02T04:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T16:35:48.000Z","uid":172192,"like":111,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"c346e6d1faee8e9efe61e6c7cb3b603704aa36f5","tid":1857123,"uid":172192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"唔知點解班黃絲豬好似都會將普選自動忽略咁<br />\n只要有關普選嘅話題就會沉得好快<br />\n同港獨一樣係勢在必行只係先後次序問題<br />\n莫講話五大訴求 基本上想解決任何問題只要成功落實普選先能夠辦到<br />\n<br />\n但成班都淨係識得叫口號屌警黑進攻體制內呢啲不着邊際嘅動作<br />\n因為今次嘅運動先接觸政治嘅人好多<br />\n而更多嘅係盲目聽從某部份KOL政客公眾人物嘅說話<br />\n將批判同思考過程假手於人 冇一張屬於自己嘅雲圖<br />\n<br />\n而可謂真正覺醒咗嘅人都死嘅死傷嘅傷<br />\n當然每一位手足嘅付出點都有佢嘅作用<br />\n但諗清楚到底每個轉捩點係因為咩重大原因而造成<br />\n衝擊立法會阻擋二讀 港大理大戰加速通過人權法<br />\n直到而家美國將香港嘅民主加入貿易協議<br />\n如果我哋今鋪仲唔乘勝追擊落實普選<br />\n真係難保再有下個機會可以成功"},{"pid":"d33237eb6e61b527cef55475542824dd66bfd2a2","tid":1857123,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"d0297e3d28acd972882f09f339e7701db762ce1b","tid":1857123,"uid":269061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:51:19.000Z","msg":"蕭生：「你唔封我封」行動正式上線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1856903\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1856903</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c86f3de656759924afae5a2d49babc3c453bda5a","tid":1857123,"uid":28818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n香港又有歷史古蹟俾政府拆喇 嘈過石獅子 深水埗警署嘅人去咗邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857079</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c51d91ff0be0c0fdea5e8e0c2b6218cc4bf6fc1f","tid":1857123,"uid":172192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9569711e90330ef7f3c632ac5dfdcc9cc8b15214","tid":1857123,"uid":28818,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:53:13.000Z","msg":"香港公民意識太弱 同埋冇政治意識/頭腦<br />\n普通人除咗大學讀相關嘅科<br />\n好少會接觸類似嘅嘢 即係政治啊嗰啲<br />\n長期被灌輸一個概念 政治好複雜政治好邪惡<br />\n<br />\n香港又有歷史古蹟俾政府拆喇 嘈過石獅子 深水埗警署嘅人去咗邊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857079</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"239d9c007c8c406855fc4912534b7538b5d5f8f8","tid":1857123,"uid":205552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:54:09.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"d3169557289b3d530f6f010654a0824fa36f80c6","tid":1857123,"uid":205552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:54:29.000Z","msg":"冇普選乜都係假"},{"pid":"a10b328669173e8dc8b0abc007ee51d304029ebf","tid":1857123,"uid":172192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"認同請幫手推 我地冇時間啦"},{"pid":"a5562a19fb06fc1f64f05ba9e4b7ecd97c3b714b","tid":1857123,"uid":172192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:05:23.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"867419d891a86e87d5c323d32b3ce211cacf7066","tid":1857123,"uid":61287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:08:36.000Z","msg":"無普選，另外個四個訴求隨時係假"},{"pid":"2b3350d9d5586a4c21362a58f991653015f53f2e","tid":1857123,"uid":172192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"58056bccb5141730dd6b090fafb3a9d1b474131f","tid":1857123,"uid":172192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"普選PO真係推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5238bea1406c891b705a59f8934e95f8c8c14e8e","tid":1857123,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f20ffdceffbe8b3d96220e7001a1695cb360f0a7","tid":1857123,"uid":339117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"Um岩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b361370160ad5f0a51ee6c7291cd971fc089f31","tid":